{"id":4386,"date":"2018-03-21T17:08:06","date_gmt":"2018-03-21T21:08:06","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/staging.cegepsl.qc.ca\/nouvelle\/de-la-creation-la-publication\/"},"modified":"2023-06-14T13:18:46","modified_gmt":"2023-06-14T17:18:46","slug":"de-la-creation-la-publication","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/nouvelle\/de-la-creation-la-publication\/","title":{"rendered":"De la cr\u00e9ation \u00e0 la publication"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Dans le cadre de la s\u00e9rie lire \u00e0 l&rsquo;ann\u00e9e, nous accueillons Marie-No\u00eblle Gagnon, auteure et \u00e9ditrice.<!--more--><\/p>\n<p>Marie-No\u00eblle Gagnon, \u00e9ditrice chez Qu\u00e9bec Am\u00e9rique, a aussi publi\u00e9 deux romans, ainsi que deux ouvrages jeunesse. Elle viendra s&rsquo;entretenir avec nous du monde de l&rsquo;\u00e9dition, de la r\u00e9ception critique des \u0153uvres litt\u00e9raires au Qu\u00e9bec et du processus de cr\u00e9ation. Elle pourra aussi r\u00e9pondre \u00e0 toutes vos questions concernant \u00ab\u00a0Le Grand Galop\u00a0\u00bb, r\u00e9cipiendaire du prix Jacques-Poirier 2016.<\/p>\n<p>Rendez-vous vendredi le 23 mars 2018 \u00e0 11 heures!<br \/>\nLocal C-5<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Dans le cadre de la s\u00e9rie LIRE \u00c0 L&rsquo;ANN\u00c9E, nous accueillons Marie-No\u00eblle Gagnon, auteure et \u00e9ditrice.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":4387,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[15],"sujet-actualite":[],"etiquette-interne":[],"class_list":["post-4386","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-nouvelle"],"acf":[],"publishpress_future_action":{"enabled":false,"date":"2026-05-04 22:33:28","action":"change-status","newStatus":"draft","terms":[],"taxonomy":"category"},"publishpress_future_workflow_manual_trigger":{"enab